oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grocer's housing
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the two-story building housing J.H. Jones, grocer. People are standing on the porch next to dry goods, and there are two children on the left edge of the porch. Boys with horse-drawn buggies are on both sides of the store.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
